room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by La Crosse Escape Room in La Crosse
review: We did the bank heist room and it was amazing. Very well thought out and we will definitely be back for more.

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by La Crosse Escape Room in La Crosse
review: Fantastic time, went through the serial killer scenario and was having a blast with it. Would do this again.

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by La Crosse Escape Room in La Crosse
review: Tons of fun. We did the bank heist and almost made it through the whole thing. We were a group of four and I thought it was the perfect amount of people. Definitely worth going back and trying the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by La Crosse Escape Room in La Crosse
review: We had a fun time trying the Bank Heist. It was a fun experience and was a great way to bond on a Father's Day! We can't wait to come back and try the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by La Crosse Escape Room in La Crosse
review: Went with family and had an absolute blast!!! Highly recommend Bank Heist, especially if you have some more experienced players in your group. Staff was very personable and fun. Room was simple at first glance but very creative. Thanks for an awesome night and lots of laughs!
